# Resume File

请将您的个人简历 PDF 命名为 `resume.pdf`，并放在此目录下。

Place your resume PDF file here and name it `resume.pdf`.

---

## 如何替换 / How to Replace

1. 将您的 PDF 简历文件重命名为 `resume.pdf`
2. 将其复制到此目录下，替换占位文件
3. 提交并推送到 GitHub

1. Rename your PDF resume to `resume.pdf`
2. Copy it to this directory, replacing the placeholder
3. Commit and push to GitHub

---

## 链接说明 / Link Info

网站中「Download Resume」按钮会自动链接到此文件：
`./resume/resume.pdf`

The "Download Resume" button in the website links to:
`./resume/resume.pdf`
